org.objectrepository.instruction
[Groovy] Class Instruction

java.lang.Object
  org.objectrepository.instruction.Tasking
      org.objectrepository.instruction.Instruction

class Instruction
extends Tasking

Instruction Stand alone object. It has children... Stagingfile and Task. We will not add a hasMany relation as it uses the dbref object. Although in itself that may not be a problem; there is the 4MB document limit to consider with many file references reaching that limit easily. Hence we use the fileSet as key to relate the Instruction document and Stagingfile documents
